      <title>英伟达本周暴跌 4060 亿美元，比特币却显得平静</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nvidia-s-400-billion-tumble-this-week-makes-bitcoin-look-calm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国经济健康状况的担忧以及可能已经超前的人工智能交易，英伟达公司本周市值蒸发了约 4060 亿美元，给主要股市基准带来压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/nvidia-s-400-billion-tumble-this-week-makes-bitcoin-look-calm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 18:03:18 GMT</pubDate>
